### TITLE ###
Homebrew_FormulaTestScript
### DESCRIPTION ###
Mirrors the test script in the homebrew-core formula (Formula/r/rad.rb).
If this test breaks, the homebrew formula test will also break.
Update both together.
### INPUT ###
args:
    times int = 1

for _ in range(times):
    print("Hello, Homebrew!")
### ARGS ###
2
### STDOUT ###
Hello, Homebrew!
Hello, Homebrew!

